sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API
    participant Database

    Client->>API: DELETE /carts/{cartId}/items/{itemId}
    API->>Database: DELETE FROM cart_items WHERE id = $1 AND cart_id = $2 RETURNING id
    Database-->>API: deleted row id (or not found)
    alt item not found
        API-->>Client: 404 Not Found (ProblemDetail)
    else item removed
        API-->>Client: 204 No Content
    end
